    <date day="01" month="November" year="2004"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a mechanism of using BGP for the discovery of
L2VPN membership information. The L2VPN membership information can be
used by a L2VPN signaling protocol to set up pseudowires for L2VPNs, such as VPWS and VPLS.
	 </t>
